msgctxt "180_Minoru"
msgid "Oh, Kiryu-san."
msgstr "Oh, Kiryu-san."

msgctxt "192_Kiryu"
msgid "You found his contact lenses?"
msgstr "¿Has encontrado sus lentillas?"

msgctxt "204_Minoru"
msgid "Yeah, thanks to you!"
msgstr "¡Sí, gracias a usted!"

msgctxt "216_Kiryu"
msgid "That's good."
msgstr "Genial."

msgctxt "228_Minoru"
msgid "The mother of that lost little girl came by for her, too. She said to tell you thank you."
msgstr "La madre de esa niña perdida también vino a por ella. Me dijo que le diera las gracias a usted."

msgctxt "240_Kiryu"
msgid "Great."
msgstr "Bien."

msgctxt "252_Kiryu"
msgid "Is this the purse that was stolen from you?"
msgstr "Disculpe, señora. ¿Es este el bolso que le robaron?"

msgctxt "276_Elderly Woman"
msgid "That's it! Let me look inside."
msgstr "¡Sí! Déjeme mirar dentro."

msgctxt "288_Elderly Woman"
msgid "Thank goodness! The fountain pen from my husband is still here. I don't know how I can ever thank you!"
msgstr "¡Menos mal! La pluma estilográfica de mi marido todavía está aquí. ¡No sé cómo agradecérselo!"

msgctxt "300_Kiryu"
msgid "Don't worry about it. I couldn't just sit back and let your purse get taken."
msgstr "No se preocupe por eso. No podía dejar que el tipo saliera impune."

msgctxt "312_Elderly Woman"
msgid "Thank you so much. Take care, young man!"
msgstr "Muchísimas gracias. ¡Cuídese, joven!"

msgctxt "372_Kiryu"
msgid "Let's see. Guess that takes care of everything. Let's go find Saya."
msgstr "Veamos. Supongo que eso es todo. Busquemos a Saya."

msgctxt "384_Minoru"
msgid "Right!"
msgstr "¡Voy!"

